          "reviewTitle": "Perfect concealer!",
          "reviewText": "I LOVE this concealer! No weird smells. Goes on smooth, and the doe foot applicator is soft and easy to use. Color blends so nicely and matches my skin perfectly! I don\u2019t just use it to conceal, but as a pseudo foundation as well! I don\u2019t wear much makeup, and so I blend this from my eyelids and under them, down the rest of my face. There\u2019s no lines of demarcation to indicate that I didn\u2019t apply it to the whole of my face either. Blurs pores nicely and doesn\u2019t cause my wrinkles to be more noticeable either. Super great price! Would recommend!!",
